import csv
f = open('age_gender.csv')
data = csv.reader(f)
m = []
f = []
name = input('궁금한 동네를 입력해주세요 : ')
for row in data :
    if name in row[0] :
        for i in range(3,104) : 
            m.append(int(row[i]))
            f.append(int(row[i+103]))        
        break
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
plt.figure(dpi = 300)
plt.rc('font', family = 'Malgun Gothic')
plt.style.use('ggplot')
plt.title(name + ' 연령별 남녀 인구수 비교')
plt.plot(m, label = '남성')
plt.plot(f, label = '여성')
plt.legend()
plt.show()

import csv
f = open('age_gender.csv')
data = csv.reader(f)
result = []
name = input('궁금한 동네를 입력해주세요 : ')
for row in data :
    if name in row[0] :
        for i in range(3,104) : 
            result.append(int(row[i]) - int(row[i+103]))
        break

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
plt.figure(dpi = 300)
plt.rc('font', family = 'Malgun Gothic')
plt.style.use('ggplot')
plt.title('제주특별자치도의 연령별 남녀 인구수 비교')
plt.rcParams['axes.unicode_minus'] = False
plt.bar(range(101), result)
plt.show()

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import random
x = []
y = []
size = []
for i in range(100) : 
    x.append(random.randint(50,100))
    y.append(random.randint(50,100))
    size.append(random.randint(10,100))
plt.figure(dpi = 300)
plt.style.use('ggplot')
plt.scatter(x, y, s = size)
plt.show()

import csv

data = csv.reader(f)
m = []
f = []
age = []
name = input('궁금한 동네를 입력해주세요 : ')
for row in data :
    if name in row[0] :
        for i in range(3,104) : 
            m.append(int(row[i]))

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

import csv
import math
f = open('age_gender.csv')
data = csv.reader(f)
m = []
f = []
size = []
name = input('궁금한 동네를 입력해주세요 : ')
for row in data :
    if name in row[0] :
        for i in range(3,104) : 
            m.append(int(row[i]))
            f.append(int(row[i+103]))
            size.append(math.sqrt(int(row[i]) + int(row[i+103])))
        break
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
plt.style.use('ggplot')
plt.rc('font',family='Malgun Gothic')
plt.figure(figsize = (10,5), dpi=300)            
plt.title(name+' 지역의 성별 인구 그래프')
plt.scatter(m, f, s = size, c = range(101), alpha=0.5, cmap='jet')
plt.colorbar()
plt.plot(range(max(m)),range(max(m)), 'g')
plt.xlabel('남성 인구수')
plt.ylabel('여성 인구수')
plt.show()

import csv
f = open('age_gender.csv')
data = csv.reader(f)
next(data)
for row in data :
    m = []
    f = []
    size = []
    name = row[0]
    for i in range(3,104) : 
        m.append(int(row[i]))
        f.append(int(row[i+103]))
        size.append(math.sqrt(int(row[i]) + int(row[i+103])) * 4)
        
    import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
    plt.style.use('ggplot')
    plt.rc('font',family='Malgun Gothic')
    plt.figure(figsize = (10,5), dpi=300)            
    plt.title(name+' 지역의 성별 인구 그래프')
    plt.scatter(m, f, s = size, c = range(101), alpha=0.5, cmap='jet')
    plt.colorbar()
    plt.plot(range(max(m)),range(max(m)), 'g')
    plt.show()

import csv
f = open('age_gender.csv')
data = csv.reader(f)
next(data)
for row in data :
    m = []
    f = []
    name = row[0]
    for i in range(3,104) : 
        m.append(int(row[i]))
        f.append(int(row[i+103]))

    import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
    plt.style.use('ggplot')
    plt.rc('font',family='Malgun Gothic')
    plt.figure(figsize = (10,5), dpi=300)            
    plt.title(name+' 지역의 성별 인구 그래프')
    plt.scatter(m, f, c = range(101), alpha=0.5, cmap='jet')
    plt.colorbar()
    plt.plot(range(max(m)),range(max(m)), 'g')
    plt.savefig(name+' 지역의 성별 인구 그래프.png')
    plt.show()
